About Sena - Guardians Of The Nation: This story follows the bond between father Deen Dayal Sharma and son Kartik Sharma. Kartik leaves a good job in California to join the Indian Army, despite his father‚Äôs opposition. After clearing the CDS exam and SSB interview, he becomes a Captain posted in Kashmir. Their tense relationship and Kartik's SSB journey are shown in flashbacks. When militants attack and capture them, Kartik pretends to cooperate to plan an escape, sending a secret message to the Army. They flee through the jungle, and after a mishap, Kartik returns to India to lead a mission against the terrorist base.

snippet.title: Maa Jaye - Trailer | Jimmy Sheirgill | Manav Vij | Yograj Singh | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
From the makers of heartfelt Punjabi cinema comes a story of Brothers love, sacrifice, and unbreakable bonds. Maa Jaye follows the journey of Brotherhood, family, and the struggles that test the limits of relationships.

"Maa Jaye" in cinemas on 29th August 2025.

Starring - Jimmy Sheirgill, Manav Vij, Yograj Singh
Introducing - Rehmat Rattan

Producer - Dr Amarjit Singh
Director - Navaniat Singh
Associate Director - Gurpreet Singh Guri, Vk Singh Mom.
Original Idea - Jacqueline Christiano
Screenplay Adaptation - Inderpal Singh
Dialogues and Additional Screenplay - Gurpreet Sehji
Music - Jaidev Kumar
Cinematographer - Jitan Harmeet Singh
Editor - Rohit Dhiman
Trailer Mix - Deepak Poojari (Afterplay Studios )
Production Designer - Shree
Costumes - Tejinder Kaur
Visual Promotions - Visual Key Studios
Music Distribution - Desi Melodies
